; Regression test for issue #725: Output of cleared not aligned with --date-format (BZ#725)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/725
; The separator line at the bottom of 'cleared' output should match the
; width of the date column, but it is fixed at 9 dashes regardless of
; the --date-format in use.

2024/01/01 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test cleared --date-format '%Y-%m-%d'
         $-10.00             $-10.00    2024-01-01    Assets:Cash
          $10.00              $10.00    2024-01-01    Expenses:Food
----------------    ----------------    ---------
               0                   0             
end test
